fr.dabsunter.darkour.api

Class ParkourBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.dabsunter.darkour.api.ParkourBuilder

  • public class ParkourBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    ParkourBuilder is designed to easely and safely create and register new Parkours in the Darkour plugin without breaking everything
